- If a rule's pattern is "javax.ejb.Stateless", your code must use javax.ejb.Stateless — not a made-up alternative.
- For Go rules: the import path in the pattern (e.g., "golang.org/x/crypto/md4") must appear as an actual import in your code. Use a real function or type from that package.
